# GhostFactory Agent Store — Cursor Rules

## Skill Usage
Before every task, check skills/ and agents/ directories.
Read SKILL.md of any skill with 1%+ chance of helping the task.

## Skills available
- skills/web-search/SKILL.md — research, fact-checking
- skills/file-ops/SKILL.md — file operations
- skills/browser/SKILL.md — web automation
- skills/email/SKILL.md — email operations

## Agents available
- agents/analytik/ — data analysis
- agents/creator/ — content creation
- agents/auditor/ — QA and review
- agents/strategist/ — strategy and planning
- agents/browser-agent/ — web scraping

## Language
All code comments, prompts, and agent instructions: English.
UI strings: messages/ folder (EN + CS).

## Models
Use model_config.yaml aliases. Never hardcode model strings.
